name: Gang Tetris
body:
# Gang Tetris Game

Gang Tetris is a multiplayer version of classical tetris.

# Scalability

Linked by [RabbitMQ](https://www.rabbitmq.com), shipped [Docker](https://www.docker.com/) — this application can be scaled horizontally.
